 Wednesday 14.3.17 Kit inspect . Went to pierrot show at night . Thursday 15.3.17 More bearer to stand by in readi to go to line ; expect to go at ani time now ; do n't expect to get the leav grant me under the circumst Friday 16.3.17 Close camp , owe to have to stand by . My leav cancel Saturday 17.3.17 Heavi bombard dure night . 20 men left for the line at 7.15 Am Ordere to move of at 7 Am in the morn . Bapaum captur earli this morn . Sunday 18.3.17 Further detail re take of Bapaum
